cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with computer vision techniques and deep learning for estimating the surface area and volume of an object (ham) through a camera. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning features, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves mathematical analysis, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves video analysis, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
